	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Nes 50/60hz workaround?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Overclocking will increase frame rate, but it will make lines shorter and line count will be 312. You need same length lines but only 262 of them for 60Hz video output.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


